ActConflict of Interest Act
SubjectHonourable Marc Gold - Public Office Holder
PrecisOrder designating the Hon. MARC GOLD, Senator from Quebec, as a PUBLIC OFFICE HOLDER (1) for the purpose of paragraph (e) of the definition public office holder in subsection 2(1) of CONFLICT OF INTEREST ACT; and (2) as a REPORTING PUBLIC OFFICE HOLDER holder for the purpose of paragraph (f) of the definition reporting public office holder in subsection 2(1) of the CONFLICT OF INTEREST ACT.
